<p>&#8220;我不能承認這些矮子是有很高文化的人，但是拿貓人和他們比，貓人也許比他們更低一些。<br />
I can&#8217;t admit that those midgets have a very high culture. But compared with them, the cats are even worse.<br />
無論怎說，這些矮人必是有個，假如沒有別的好處，國家觀念。<br />
Whatever you say, this midgets have, even if they don&#8217;t have anything else to say for them, they have a concept of country.<br />
國家觀念不過是擴大的自私，可是它到底是“擴大”的；貓人只知道自己。&#8221;<br />
The concept of country is nothing else than an extension of the ego. But at least it&#8217;s an extension. The cats know nothing but themselves.</p>
